Differential comparisions...
| **Feature**                | **Description**                                                      |
| -------------------------- | -------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| Modular Bluetooth Design   | Bluetooth PCB separated from headphone drivers                       |
| High-Capacity Battery      | Upgraded from the original battery to a 1500 mAh Li-ion battery      |
| USB Type-C Charging        | Modern charging connector replacing the original Micro-USB interface |
| High-Quality Audio Drivers | Uses Sennheiser HD 202 professional dynamic drivers                  |
| Component Reusability      | Legacy Bluetooth PCB repurposed instead of discarded                 |
| Repair-Friendly Design     | Easy access to battery, charging module, and Bluetooth PCB           |
| Wired Audio Connection     | Stable connection between Bluetooth module and headphone drivers     |
| Sustainable Design         | Promotes electronic waste reduction through hardware reuse           |
| Lightweight Prototype      | Compact external Bluetooth control module                            |
| Future Upgrade Support     | Designed for hardware expansion and modification                     |

